'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2983] on 8 November 2000 at 8:09:23 pm'!"Change Set:		DangerAheadDate:			8 November 2000Author:			Andreas RaabCross your fingers..."!"Postscript:Warn of major impending changes."(self confirm: 'The next bunch of updates include a complete reimplementation of Morphic''slayout handling and all related aspects.- - -WARNING: It is likely that any projects you store after receiving this updateand before some (yet to come) cleanup update MAY NOT WORK once the changeshave been completed. So unless you have very good reason to, the best choice may be to wait until an ''all clear'' message comes out. If you wish to stop here,choose ''no'', close the resulting notifier, and save your image if you wish toretain the other updates so far.- - -If you wish to press on, then cross your fingers, and choose ''yes''.')	ifFalse: ["Prevent advancement of version number."			Smalltalk changes name: 'updateBumper' , (Time millisecondClockValue \\ 99999) printString.			self halt: 'You may close this window.'].!